headline: Align Technology’s Invisalign® Brand Announces Official Sponsorship of Bay FC
summary: SAN FRANCISCO & SAN JOSE, Calif., March 25, 2025--Bay FC and Align Technology today announced that Align Technology’s Invisalign® brand is an Official Partner of Bay FC.
